{"snp2.8:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 2.8 ","snp2.8:0.2":"Dhamma (nava) sutta ","snp2.8:1.1":"Yasma hi dhammam puriso vijanna, ","snp2.8:1.2":"Indamva nam devata pujayeyya; ","snp2.8:1.3":"So pujito tasmi pasannacitto, ","snp2.8:1.4":"Bahussuto patukaroti dhammam. ","snp2.8:2.1":"Tadatthikatvana nisamma dhiro, ","snp2.8:2.2":"Dhammanudhammam patipajjamano; ","snp2.8:2.3":"Vinnu vibhavi nipuno ca hoti, ","snp2.8:2.4":"Yo tadisam bhajati appamatto. ","snp2.8:3.1":"Khuddanca balam upasevamano, ","snp2.8:3.2":"Anagatatthanca usuyakanca; ","snp2.8:3.3":"Idheva dhammam avibhavayitva, ","snp2.8:3.4":"Avitinnakankho maranam upeti. ","snp2.8:4.1":"Yatha naro apagamotaritva, ","snp2.8:4.2":"Mahodakam salilam sighasotam; ","snp2.8:4.3":"So vuyhamano anusotagami, ","snp2.8:4.4":"Kim so pare sakkhati tarayetum. ","snp2.8:5.1":"Tatheva dhammam avibhavayitva, ","snp2.8:5.2":"Bahussutanam anisamayattham; ","snp2.8:5.3":"Sayam ajanam avitinnakankho, ","snp2.8:5.4":"Kim so pare sakkhati nijjhapetum. ","snp2.8:6.1":"Yathapi navam dalhamaruhitva, ","snp2.8:6.2":"Phiyena rittena samangibhuto; ","snp2.8:6.3":"So taraye tattha bahupi anne, ","snp2.8:6.4":"Tatrupayannu kusalo mutima. ","snp2.8:7.1":"Evampi yo vedagu bhavitatto, ","snp2.8:7.2":"Bahussuto hoti avedhadhammo; ","snp2.8:7.3":"So kho pare nijjhapaye pajanam, ","snp2.8:7.4":"Sotavadhanupanisupapanne. ","snp2.8:8.1":"Tasma have sappurisam bhajetha, ","snp2.8:8.2":"Medhavinanceva bahussutanca; ","snp2.8:8.3":"Annaya attham patipajjamano, ","snp2.8:8.4":"Vinnatadhammo sa sukham labhethati. ","snp2.8:8.5":"Navasuttam atthamam. "}